						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up in a field outside the village.</p>						

						<p>13th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription in characters of about 13th century A.D. is dated in the cyclic year Dundubhi. Seems to record the death of a person and the setting up of the memorial stone.</p>						

